{"tid":1533654,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"太子彌敦道被捕男子被警員不合理地對待","createTime":"2019-09-02T18:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T19:51:14.000Z","uid":120066,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd71210b177413bd2c9db7e8d1d740e54dad7186","tid":1533654,"uid":120066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:46:10.000Z","msg":"第一次發文，如果有錯字請見諒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為朋友無連登帳號，所以唯有代朋友出文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKNqYdZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKNqYdZ.png&h=2ca980e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中嘅男仔係我朋友嘅同學，首先係到同大家交代翻已經搵左律司去跟進個男仔情況，個男仔暫時都係廣華醫院。<br />\n<br />\n然而個男仔當時顯然係無裝備、無攻擊性，更加莫講話觸犯任何事情，但都被警察使用不合理嘅武力去制服並逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫忙將事情備份，日後去追究呢幾個月包括其中呢件事所有使用不合理武力嘅警察。<br />\n<br />\n最後附上同朋友嘅對話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEGfA4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEGfA4q.png&h=2b9c221e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9bca0e18167fbf640bf56bb5abebfde996f3d2c9","tid":1533654,"uid":120066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:46:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c755c39164eeabed13c8ce25d059ba08c4e4001","tid":1533654,"uid":120066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b43bd921ba95993987cb3efc3bfdabaa90911852","tid":1533654,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以話我聽佢人無事嘛"},{"pid":"fd55a97a921b64035e4db618b1e213fea202331b","tid":1533654,"uid":120066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:48:20.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dc42d95f1099c1c36a7d19eeb480d71589fa9a","tid":1533654,"uid":80851,"like